Key Account Manager Job (Consumer Goods), Jakarta, Indonesia  -
Key Account Manager Job (Consumer Goods), Jakarta, Indonesia
Responsibilities
Monroe Consulting Group is recruiting on behalf of one of the largest-independent owners and operators of towers for wireless operators in Indonesia. Its core business is leasing space at its multi-tenant towers for all major wireless operators in Indonesia under long-term lease agreements. Our client is seeking a sales and marketing professional for the job of Key Account Manager, to be based in Jakarta, Indonesia. Key job responsibilities will include: Identify potential new business opportunitiesAgenda of the corporate plan with other telecom companies, both in terms of business and technicalNegotiate business and forge cooperation with telecommunications operatorsResolve domestic and international co-operation agreementsResolve issues that occur regarding interconnection and leased-lines Job Requirements Candidate must possess at least a Bachelor's degree, any field.At least 8 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this positionHealthy and willing to travel around IndonesiaHighly skilled in salesmanship and leadershipFluent in EnglishGood report writing skillsExcellent strategic business and analytical skillsGood presentation, communication and negotiation skillsAble to deliver timely and quality results under limited supervision All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence. If you are a suitable match for this position please send your application to technology@monroeconsulting.com
